<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.7">
<l>maṉṉañ cavāyirantōḷ maḻuviṟṟu ṇittamaintā</l>
<l>veṉneñ cattuḷḷirun tiṅkiṉippōyp piṟaroruvar</l>
<l>vaṉṉeñ campukkirukka voṭṭēṉva ḷaittuvaittēṉ</l>
<l>naṉṉeñ cavaṉṉamaṉṉum naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Young man who severed with an axe one-thousand arms</l>
<l rend="indent">to frighten the kings,</l>
<l>Having been in my heart, going here and now, I cannot allow</l>
<l>That you keep entering the firm hearts of any others; I have captured [you],</l>
<l>O Noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr, where abides the swan of good heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
